				</label>
				<br><br><br>
				<p>
					The Bible speaks about lust in 2 Timothy 2:22, “Flee also youthful lusts; but pursue righteousness, faith, love [and] peace...” <br>

					The Bible also mentions lust in the following verses: Job 31:1, Matthew 5:28, Philippians 4:8, James 1:14-15, 1 Peter 2:11 and 1 John 2:16. <br>

					Chastity or self-control cures lust by controlling passion and leveraging that energy for the good of others. <br>

